## Animation Guidelines

### ✅ DO: Use consistent motion patterns
```tsx
// Page entrance
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
  animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.6 }}
>

// Staggered animations
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 30 }}
  animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.6, delay: index * 0.1 }}
>

// Hover effects
<div className="group cursor-pointer">
  <div className="transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105">
    {/* Hover content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

## Accessibility

### ✅ DO: Use proper semantic HTML
```tsx
<main className="flex-1">
  <section className="mb-16">
    <h2 className="text-3xl font-serif text-terracotta-600">
      Section Title
    </h2>
  </section>
</main>
```

### ✅ DO: Use proper ARIA labels
```tsx
<button 
  className="md:hidden p-2 text-dark-teal-700 hover:text-vibrant-pink-600 transition-colors" 
  aria-label="Toggle mobile menu"
>
  <svg>...</svg>
</button>
```